feeling that the treatments were less tormenting.

27
00:02:34,210 --> 00:02:36,710
Read this. It's her message.

28
00:02:36,710 --> 00:02:38,670
 Dear Brother Qiao Yi.

29
00:02:38,670 --> 00:02:39,690
 Hi.

30
