89
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,720
 Twenty-five years old.

90
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:45,750
 But, I want you to accompany me to a place.

91
00:06:45,750 --> 00:06:47,220
Rooftop?

92
00:06:47,220 --> 00:06:49,720
I can take pictures of your dead body.

93
