127
00:08:34,350 --> 00:08:36,130
You have done a good job!

128
00:08:36,130 --> 00:08:40,090
Kevin, call our attorney to see if we have sent any letters

129
00:08:40,090 --> 00:08:42,620
or released any announcements about that picture.

130
00:08:42,620 --> 00:08:44,970
All right, I'll call him right away.

131
00:08:53,290 --> 00:08:54,980
All right.

132
00:08:54,980 --> 00:08:57,330
President Ji, the attorney said we released an announcement,

133
00:08:57,330 --> 00:09:00,510
