150
00:10:12,620 --> 00:10:14,740
It's too complicated.

151
00:10:14,740 --> 00:10:17,440
I don't think I can explain this to you in a few words.

152
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,980
If you like my book,

153
00:10:18,980 --> 00:10:22,680
I'll bring my new book to you later.

154
00:10:24,990 --> 00:10:26,480
But

155
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:30,910
I am not the only one who's expecting your new book.

156
00:10:39,150 --> 00:10:42,230
Every time when you launch a new book,

157
00:10:42,230 --> 00:10:45,230
your stories warm me

158
00:10:45,230 --> 00:10:47,300
and so many others up.

159
00:10:47,300 --> 00:10:51,670
Your stories even moved my mom.

160
00:10:54,220 --> 00:10:57,040
Am I right, Brother Li Ang?

161
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:59,490
Totally.

162
00:10:59,490 --> 00:11:04,090
Brother Qiao Yi's story can always bring light to people

163
00:11:04,090 --> 00:11:09,050
at their saddest or worst moments.

164
00:11:10,700 --> 00:11:13,690
The sunshine on a winter night? Am I?

165
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:18,550
I didn't tell you for fear that you might get too cocky.

166
00:11:18,550 --> 00:11:20,650
When am I even cocky?

167
00:11:20,650 --> 00:11:23,150
Totally nonsense.

168
00:11:32,450 --> 00:11:34,010
I get it now.

169
00:11:34,010 --> 00:11:35,680
I was being so self-willed

170
