221
00:16:35,570 --> 00:16:37,480
Wait.

222
00:16:40,880 --> 00:16:44,130
Jiang Hanyi and I have known each other since childhood.

223
00:16:45,050 --> 00:16:46,950
After my parents died,

224
00:16:46,950 --> 00:16:51,080
half of my life was spent at her home.

225
00:16:52,810 --> 00:16:55,910
She and her parents

226
00:16:55,910 --> 00:16:59,220
treat Nian Nian and me like family.

227
00:17:01,390 --> 00:17:04,180
So to me,

228
00:17:04,180 --> 00:17:06,950
she is also a family.

229
00:17:06,950 --> 00:17:09,960
She's like my second sister after Nian Nian.

230
00:17:14,560 --> 00:17:17,350
W-Why did you say these to me?

231
00:17:17,350 --> 00:17:19,160
It has nothing to do with me.

232
00:17:19,160 --> 00:17:21,270
Sounds so ridiculous.

233
00:17:27,340 --> 00:17:28,970
Zhou Tian,

234
00:17:31,510 --> 00:17:34,180
I did make mistakes.

235
00:17:35,510 --> 00:17:37,420
I want to apologize to you.

236
00:17:38,790 --> 00:17:40,520
Apologize?

237
00:17:40,520 --> 00:17:42,710
Too late!

238
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:51,770
Can we restart this?

239
00:17:52,920 --> 00:17:55,550
I'll prove to you

240
00:17:55,550 --> 00:17:58,070
