Why don't you give us some advice?

275
00:21:14,530 --> 00:21:17,780
Me? Really?

276
00:21:17,780 --> 00:21:21,530
But I'm not professional in the band.

277
00:21:21,530 --> 00:21:24,930
You think Li Ang is? He's not professional, either.

278
00:21:24,930 --> 00:21:28,310
Music is a matter of joy. Come in.

