00:21:51,950 --> 00:21:58,380

285
00:22:02,650 --> 00:22:04,360
Hello?

286
00:22:04,360 --> 00:22:06,380
 Quick! Check the trending topics!

287
00:22:07,180 --> 00:22:08,840
Hold on.

288
00:22:09,640 --> 00:22:12,540

289
00:22:12,540 --> 00:22:13,620

290
00:22:16,340 --> 00:22:17,510
What's going on?

291
00:22:17,510 --> 00:22:20,590
It's said that Extreme Impala's developers once invested in Xing Yi's project.

292
00:22:20,590 --> 00:22:22,180
 What?

293
00:22:22,180 --> 00:22:28,500

294
00:22:28,500 --> 00:22:34,000

295
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:36,670
 This news is spreading quickly.

296
00:22:36,670 --> 00:22:39,550
 Now, it has affected the share price of our company.

297
00:22:39,550 --> 00:22:41,770
 Do you have any solution?

298
00:22:41,770 --> 00:22:45,170
I have asked someone to investigate all of our external cooperation contracts.

299
00:22:45,170 --> 00:22:49,160
There isn't any business contract between Xing Yi and Extreme Impala.

300
00:22:49,160 --> 00:22:51,920
Everything on the Internet is a rumor.

301
00:22:51,920 --> 00:22:55,400
I have asked the Legal Department to handle this matter.

302
00:22:55,400 --> 00:22:58,890
 There are many people who want you to resign.

303
00:22:58,890 --> 00:23:01,560
 This rumor spreads too quickly.

304
00:23:01,560 --> 00:23:04,290
 And the comments on the Internet are to your disadvantage.

305
00:23:04,290 --> 00:23:08,700
 President Ji, you have to respond to this matter.

306
00:23:08,700 --> 00:23:10,420
 I don't think so.

307
00:23:10,420 --> 00:23:12,710
 Before the truth comes out,

308
00:23:12,710 --> 00:23:17,320
 President Ji shouldn't give any explanation because very few would believe his words.

309
00:23:17,320 --> 00:23:20,660

310
00:23:34,070 --> 00:23:37,500
Don't worry. President Ji can handle this matter.

311
00:23:39,380 --> 00:23:41,580
If I were you, I wouldn't be so positive.

312
00:23:41,580 --> 00:23:44,570
This scandal has a huge social effect.

313
00:23:44,570 --> 00:23:46,920
It's completely different from those showbiz affairs.

314
00:23:46,920 --> 00:23:48,820
Shut up!

315
00:23:49,420 --> 00:23:53,780
After I came to Xing Yi, I changed the process of signing the contract.

316
00:23:53,780 --> 00:23:57,510
All the contracts must be signed by the agent,

317
00:23:57,510 --> 00:24:01,720
the director of the department, the CFO, the legal personnel, and myself.

318
00:24:01,720 --> 00:24:03,350
After signing the contract,

319
00:24:03,350 --> 00:24:06,880
the Financial Department will keep a copy of it before it takes effect.

320
00:24:08,580 --> 00:24:12,930
These are all the contracts that I signed after I came to Xing Yi.

321
00:24:12,930 --> 00:24:14,150
Take a look at these.

322
00:24:14,150 --> 00:24:17,500
You will know whether I have anything to do with this matter.

323
00:24:19,130 --> 00:24:24,360
 But you are the CEO. You can follow the rules.

324
00:24:24,360 --> 00:24:28,080
 But if you want to break them, I think nobody will dare to object.

325
00:24:28,520 --> 00:24:33,530
 It's said that President Ji is very decisive in the company.

326
00:24:36,070 --> 00:24:40,210
 Now, the rumors are too strong.

327
00:24:40,210 --> 00:24:43,670
 We must give everyone an explanation.

328
00:24:51,230 --> 00:24:52,840
 How about this?

329
00:24:52,840 --> 00:24:58,250
 We'll select an acting CEO from the directors

330
00:24:58,250 --> 00:25:01,460
 before we solve this matter.

331
00:25:01,460 --> 00:25:07,340
 President Chen, I think you're very suitable for this position.

332
00:25:07,340 --> 00:25:10,940
 President Chen, I agree.

333
00:25:17,380 --> 00:25:19,360
 Xiao Jiang. Just in time.

334
00:25:19,360 --> 00:25:22,990
 We're discussing how to deal with Extreme Impala.

335
00:25:22,990 --> 00:25:24,880
I agree with you.

336
00:25:24,880 --> 00:25:27,240
Since you all believe that Ji Chen is the one to blame,

337
00:25:27,240 --> 00:25:30,810
then he can rest for some time.

338
00:25:30,810 --> 00:25:35,230
From now on, I'll be the acting CEO

339
00:25:36,450 --> 00:25:38,660
of Xing Yi.

340
00:25:44,450 --> 00:25:46,450
 You?

341
00:25:46,990 --> 00:25:49,860
 Xiao Jiang, you have just returned from abroad.

342
00:25:49,860 --> 00:25:54,550
 You're not familiar with the domestic market and businesses.

343
00:25:55,190 --> 00:25:56,760
I'm also a director of the company.

344
00:25:56,760 --> 00:25:59,560
As the CEO, I don't have to be good at everything.

345
00:25:59,560 --> 00:26:02,620
All the professional matters will be handled by more professional employees.

346
00:26:02,620 --> 00:26:08,930
Mr. Chen, are you professional enough to deal with everything?

347
00:26:16,410 --> 00:26:19,180
Ji Chen. Any objection?

348
00:26:22,310 --> 00:26:27,370
Since this is the group's decision, I won't have any objection.

349
00:26:28,040 --> 00:26:30,720
It is a group's decision, of course.

350
00:26:30,720 --> 00:26:32,580
Okay. That's settled, then.

351
00:26:32,580 --> 00:26:36,280
The meeting is over. Please continue your work.

352
00:26:37,450 --> 00:26:39,180
Thank you.

353
00:26:44,270 --> 00:26:46,210
Are you serious?

354
00:26:47,080 --> 00:26:51,730
It's better for me to become the CEO than the others.

355
00:26:51,730 --> 00:26:54,570
You're acting as if this company is yours.

356
00:26:54,570 --> 00:26:57,000
I... You...

357
00:26:57,990 --> 00:26:59,720
I help with your relationship,

358
00:26:59,720 --> 00:27:02,400
and now I even have to worry about your career.

359
00:27:02,400 --> 00:27:05,280
How can you even say that?

360
00:27:05,280 --> 00:27:08,340
You're so ungrateful. I'm sad.

361
00:27:08,340 --> 00:27:12,390
But, seriously, how should we deal with this?

362
00:27:12,390 --> 00:27:14,480
We should talk about it.

363
00:27:16,320 --> 00:27:18,730
I do have a plan.

364
00:27:20,310 --> 00:27:23,230
But I need to borrow your authority.

365
00:27:23,230 --> 00:27:24,750
I love it when you have a plan.

366
00:27:24,750 --> 00:27:27,220
Please tell us, President Ji.

367
00:27:27,820 --> 00:27:30,690
Well, this incident is not that complicated.

368
00:27:30,690 --> 00:27:32,550
We can...

369
00:27:34,500 --> 00:27:36,470
President Ji is suspended!

370
00:27:36,470 --> 00:27:37,690
The announcement is just released.

371
00:27:37,690 --> 00:27:39,740
What?

372
00:27:39,740 --> 00:27:43,680

373
00:27:45,380 --> 00:27:46,310
How could it be?

374
00:27:46,310 --> 00:27:50,760

375
00:27:50,760 --> 00:27:51,980

376
00:27:51,980 --> 00:27:53,980

377
00:27:53,980 --> 00:28:00,020

378
00:28:06,090 --> 00:28:07,990
Have you read the email?

379
00:28:07,990 --> 00:28:12,080
I hold this temporary meeting to officially explain the situation

380
00:28:12,080 --> 00:28:15,220
and arrange the following work for everyone.

381
00:28:15,220 --> 00:28:17,370
- We... 
 - Director Jiang,

382
00:28:18,370 --> 00:28:22,590
I have a question about the company's decision.

383
00:28:25,110 --> 00:28:27,260
When the Extreme Impala thing just started,

384
00:28:27,260 --> 00:28:29,240
President Ji hadn't become the CEO yet.

385
00:28:29,240 --> 00:28:33,010
Why does he have to be suspended when this incident broke out?

386
00:28:37,410 --> 00:28:39,350
Now, I am the CEO of Xing Yi.

387
00:28:39,350 --> 00:28:40,890
I'm your superior.

388
00:28:40,890 --> 00:28:43,660
I don't have to explain any of my decisions to you.

389
00:28:43,660 --> 00:28:47,600
If you have any objections, you're free to resign anytime.

390
00:28:49,030 --> 00:28:51,220
Zhou Tian, sit down.

391
00:28:51,220 --> 00:28:52,820
- I'm trying to—  
 - I know.

392
00:28:52,820 --> 00:28:54,920
Thank you. Please sit down.

393
00:28:54,920 --> 00:29:00,970
 Seriously? I'm trying to help you, but you're in favor of her?

394
00:29:01,810 --> 00:29:05,320
 Nevermind. I'm nobody to you.

395
00:29:09,170 --> 00:29:10,540
Let's continue.

396
00:29:10,540 --> 00:29:14,230
The group wants us to minimize the negative effect.

397
00:29:14,230 --> 00:29:15,990
The share price can't be affected.

398
00:29:15,990 --> 00:29:18,450
Now, I'll talk about the strategy.

399
00:29:22,410 --> 00:29:25,720
The plan for crisis management...

400
00:29:25,720 --> 00:29:26,660

401
00:29:30,020 --> 00:29:32,930

402
00:29:32,930 --> 00:29:34,760
That's all for today's meeting.

403
00:29:34,760 --> 00:29:36,570
You are dismissed.

404
00:29:59,230 --> 00:30:04,890
President Ji. I think you shouldn't leave the company before the truth comes out.

405
00:30:04,890 --> 00:30:06,350
I have been suspended.

406
00:30:06,350 --> 00:30:08,830
But this matter has nothing to do with you.

407
00:30:08,830 --> 00:30:10,600
It had nothing to do with me.

408
00:30:10,600 --> 00:30:12,740
But now, I'm the CEO of Xing Yi.

409
00:30:12,740 --> 00:30:14,980
I have to be responsible for all the projects of Xing Yi,

410
00:30:15,410 --> 00:30:17,870
including this one. I have to bear the consequence.

411
00:30:17,870 --> 00:30:20,290
That's why we have to find out the truth!

412
00:30:20,290 --> 00:30:24,370
Even if you're leaving, you can't leave like this.

413
00:30:25,370 --> 00:30:27,180
I know you worry about me,

414
00:30:27,180 --> 00:30:30,940
but Jiang Hanyi is handling this matter now.

415
00:30:30,940 --> 00:30:32,690
Worry?

416
00:30:32,690 --> 00:30:36,030
I only seek justice.

417
00:30:38,280 --> 00:30:43,000
Do you remember what I told you when Qiao Yi was in trouble?

418
00:30:44,450 --> 00:30:48,680
You have to be responsible for your position.

419
00:30:51,370 --> 00:30:53,550
I don't care. You can't leave.

420
00:30:54,480 --> 00:30:57,920
 She's so cute when she worries about me.

421
00:31:02,340 --> 00:31:03,690
All right.

422
00:31:03,690 --> 00:31:07,290
Actually, this matter...

423
00:31:07,290 --> 00:31:11,970
Kindly reminder. This is my office now.

424
00:31:11,970 --> 00:31:14,080
Director Jiang, you are just in time.

425
00:31:14,080 --> 00:31:17,540
Didn't you say during the meeting that President Ji still needs to assist with your daily work?

426
00:31:17,540 --> 00:31:20,730
So, I think he shouldn't leave for now.

427
00:31:22,550 --> 00:31:25,080
But this office belongs to the CEO.

428
00:31:25,080 --> 00:31:27,350
He has no authority to stay here anymore.

429
00:31:27,350 --> 00:31:30,430
Ji Chen, I have to follow the rules.

430
00:31:30,430 --> 00:31:32,270
I hope you will understand.

431
00:31:34,520 --> 00:31:37,280
Zhou Tian, let's get out of here.

432
00:31:38,960 --> 00:31:43,450
Besides, it's not allowed to gossip during working hours.

433
00:31:43,450 --> 00:31:46,270
This rule also applies to suspended employees.

434
00:31:52,170 --> 00:31:54,690
How was it? She was so protective of you.

435
00:31:54,690 --> 00:31:56,620
Did you enjoy it?

436
00:31:58,080 --> 00:31:59,990
You're welcome!

437
00:32:03,890 --> 00:32:05,800
Where are you going?

438
00:32:10,510 --> 00:32:11,600
Here.

439
00:32:11,600 --> 00:32:13,310
Here?

440
00:32:13,310 --> 00:32:17,080
From now on,I'll be seated here.

441
00:32:17,690 --> 00:32:19,440
This is my desk.

442
00:32:19,440 --> 00:32:21,420
Excuse me!

443
00:32:21,420 --> 00:32:24,030
Excuse me. Put it here.

444
00:32:32,280 --> 00:32:36,670
President Ji, are you joking?

445
00:32:43,620 --> 00:32:45,650
Do I look joking?

446
00:32:45,650 --> 00:32:49,210
By the way, I have just been suspended.

447
00:32:49,210 --> 00:32:50,720
You don't need to call me President Ji.

448
00:32:50,720 --> 00:32:53,420
Call me Ji Chen.

449
00:32:54,210 --> 00:32:57,950
Ji... Chen.

450
00:32:57,950 --> 00:33:02,010
If you feel weird about calling me by my full name,

451
00:33:02,620 --> 00:33:04,560
you can also call me

452
00:33:04,560 --> 00:33:06,610
Chen Chen.

453
00:33:08,610 --> 00:33:12,220
I can't believe you're still in the mood for jokes.

454
00:33:25,790 --> 00:33:27,460
Ji Chen!

455
00:33:28,280 --> 00:33:30,030
Brother Yi!

456
00:33:33,930 --> 00:33:35,710
Ji Chen.

457
00:33:37,990 --> 00:33:39,380
Ji Chen? Have you transformed?

458
00:33:39,380 --> 00:33:42,080
Brother Yi. Are you looking for Ji Chen?

459
00:33:42,080 --> 00:33:44,530
But now, I am the CEO.

460
00:33:47,040 --> 00:33:50,820
It's not a joke. Ji Chen has indeed been replaced.

461
00:33:53,070 --> 00:33:54,620
I don't know you.

462
00:33:54,620 --> 00:33:56,270
Bye.

463
00:34:00,380 --> 00:34:02,190
Zhou Tian, I read the announcement.

464
00:34:02,190 --> 00:34:05,640
Ji Chen has indeed been suspended.

465
00:34:09,030 --> 00:34:10,680
You...

466
00:34:11,930 --> 00:34:13,770
You...

467
00:34:13,770 --> 00:34:15,290
You...

468
00:34:15,290 --> 00:34:16,940
W-Why are you sitting here?

469
00:34:16,940 --> 00:34:19,000
What's wrong? What do you want?

470
00:34:19,000 --> 00:34:20,500
I do want something.

471
00:34:20,500 --> 00:34:23,600
I want to add a program about my new book to Li Ang's concert.

472
00:34:23,600 --> 00:34:25,770
We decided to do charity together.

473
00:34:25,770 --> 00:34:27,410
No problem.

474
00:34:27,950 --> 00:34:29,580
But...

475
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:33,050
but you're not the CEO anymore.

476
00:34:33,050 --> 00:34:34,500
You're still my agent, though.

477
00:34:34,500 --> 00:34:35,690
I can count on you, right?

478
00:34:35,690 --> 00:34:37,880
Li Ang also works in our company.

479
00:34:37,880 --> 00:34:40,350
It will benefit both of you if you can attend his concert.

480
00:34:40,350 --> 00:34:43,680
The company won't reject your request even though I'm not the CEO.

481
00:34:44,180 --> 00:34:46,480
Okay. That's settled, then.

482
00:34:55,450 --> 00:34:59,530
Zhou Tian, keep an eye on him.

483
00:35:01,640 --> 00:35:04,550
Ji Chen had a rather successful career.

484
00:35:04,550 --> 00:35:07,370
He has never suffered so much.

485
00:35:07,370 --> 00:35:09,910
He might seem very calm right now,

486
00:35:09,910 --> 00:35:14,500
but his heart is badly injured.

487
00:35:15,780 --> 00:35:19,160
I know this kind of man the best.

488
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:24,870
He does seem weird.

489
00:35:25,870 --> 00:35:27,390
Bye.

490
00:35:48,350 --> 00:35:50,180
Ji...

491
00:35:51,030 --> 00:35:52,330
Ji Chen.

492
00:35:52,330 --> 00:35:55,420
Do you want to go home and rest?

493
00:35:55,420 --> 00:35:57,210
Remember what you said?

494
00:35:57,210 --> 00:35:59,720
I need to stay here before the truth comes out.

495
00:35:59,720 --> 00:36:01,250
I can't leave.

496
00:36:01,250 --> 00:36:03,750
Then go to investigate.

497
00:36:03,750 --> 00:36:07,080
Don't just sit here and throw paper airplanes.

498
00:36:08,810 --> 00:36:11,280
I'm not the CEO anymore.

499
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:12,920
How can I find out the truth?

500
00:36:12,920 --> 00:36:15,870
Besides, I have never been this free

501
00:36:15,870 --> 00:36:19,650
ever since I lied for a few months as a baby after I was born.

502
00:36:19,650 --> 00:36:22,940
Since you don't want to see me, I'll leave right away.

503
00:36:22,940 --> 00:36:24,650
I...

504
00:36:24,650 --> 00:36:27,200
I didn't mean that.

505
00:36:29,430 --> 00:36:33,140
What? My brother is suspended?

506
00:36:33,140 --> 00:36:35,280
Jiang Hanyi did this to him?

507
00:36:37,140 --> 00:36:39,180
Jiang Hanyi!

508
00:36:39,180 --> 00:36:40,720
I treated her as my family!

509
00:36:40,720 --> 00:36:42,280
How could she do this to my brother?

510
00:36:42,280 --> 00:36:45,290
I thought she could be my sister-in-law!

511
00:36:51,300 --> 00:36:54,680
I mean... in the past.

512
00:36:54,680 --> 00:36:56,780
That's not important.

513
00:36:56,780 --> 00:36:59,600
The point is, my brother is so proud.

514
00:36:59,600 --> 00:37:02,410
And this is so huge a blow.

515
00:37:06,030 --> 00:37:07,870
Where is he?

516
00:37:09,510 --> 00:37:13,310
This morning, I asked him whether he wanted to go home and rest,

517
00:37:13,310 --> 00:37:16,280
and I said he had nothing to do.

518
00:37:16,280 --> 00:37:19,800
Then, he went home.

519
00:37:22,100 --> 00:37:25,730
He must feel depressed after you talked to him.

520
00:37:25,730 --> 00:37:29,830
My brother is always a busy person, and he never allows himself to be free.

521
00:37:29,830 --> 00:37:32,430
Yet you said he had nothing to do.

522
00:37:33,050 --> 00:37:36,370
Will he commit suicide?

523
00:37:37,250 --> 00:37:38,720
I don't think so.

524
00:37:38,720 --> 00:37:40,620
He tries so hard to live a healthy life,

525
00:37:40,620 --> 00:37:43,720
so he must be afraid of death.

526
00:37:46,030 --> 00:37:49,760
But, I think he's quite weird.

527
00:37:49,760 --> 00:37:53,370
He seems very normal,

528
00:37:53,370 --> 00:37:57,550
but in fact, he's deeply injured.

529
00:38:10,260 --> 00:38:13,230
Xiao Nian called me just now.

530
00:38:13,230 --> 00:38:15,970
She asked me why I suspended you.

531
00:38:15,970 --> 00:38:18,300
Zhou Tian must have told her.

532
00:38:18,300 --> 00:38:20,460
That's exactly what I expected.

533
00:38:22,660 --> 00:38:26,390
You're a professional in toying with women's hearts.

534
00:38:26,390 --> 00:38:28,710
You are the wise one.

535
00:38:28,710 --> 00:38:30,980
You used me to suspend you,

536
00:38:30,980 --> 00:38:33,730
so the mastermind behind it will be off guard.

537
00:38:33,730 --> 00:38:35,050
Then, you can clear them all.

538
00:38:35,050 --> 00:38:40,100
As for me, I can help improve your relationship with Zhou Tian.

539
00:38:40,100 --> 00:38:41,782
Impressive!

540
00:38:41,782 --> 00:38:46,382
♫  It was raining that day when you held me  ♫

541
00:38:46,382 --> 00:38:50,342
♫  A shooting star fell in my heart secretly  ♫

542
00:38:50,342 --> 00:38:54,942
♫  It found a place in your eyes and witnessed my promise to you  ♫

543
00:38:54,942 --> 00:39:00,712
♫  Eventually, it brightened my whole universe  ♫

